  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: send Funds to a contact from wallet -> no new send message is shown in the chat as well as no chat created if this is the very fisrt message\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nnew send message is shown in the chat\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nno new messages are shown in the chat\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Wallet\r\n- Tap Send\r\n- Type some valid amount, e.g. 1234\r\n- From Contacts select Jarrad\r\n- tap on Sign transaction and proceed\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: last develop\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
