    "body": "Per Jan comment:\r\nOk, so this is something which I already answered long ago (we discussed about it with @roman as well), it's basically not possible to do it with current code - you can't easily create artificial `/send` message without actually going through the bot send process, but you don't want that because you are sending through wallet\r\nWhat we really need is to ditch bot code handling sending altogether and always use just wallet for that, `/send` command will just hook into that and it will be only visual shortcut (opposed to going through wallet only)\r\n\r\nThis code rework will also help us to get /send and /request for tokens in place so i marked this as high prio however it is blocked for now as I am not clear with the swarm i should assign the issue to.\r\n\r\n@jeluard @rasom could this issue be included in any of existing swarms and taken care of? ",
